1
00:00:36,480 --> 00:00:38,720
I've seen the video Sister Hua has.

2
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:40,880
Your mother

3
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,380
was pushed off the building by Danpa.

4
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,040
Danpa.

5
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:53,720
It's time

6
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,760
to settle this score.

7
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:06,240
This devil in human skin,

8
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,520
I'll send him to hell myself.

9
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,140
Relying solely on Siam Group's power

10
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,480
won't be enough to take him down.

11
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,380
I think you understand

12
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,840
the only way to bring him down.

13
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,200
Cooperation.

14
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,760
Bury his body.

15
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,920
Don't dirty my yard.

16
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,160
Good acting, Mr. Ang.

17
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:51,800
Danpa.

18
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,039
You killed my mom

19
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,880
and Dailing's parents.

20
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,200
You're not dead?

21
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,040
How could I bear to die?

22
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,400
Shaowen,

23
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,890
what's going on?

24
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,080
Ang Wei,

25
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,680
why are you so hard to kill?

26
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,120
Why do you think that is,

27
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,320
Uncle Danpa?

28
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,000
So you two brats

29
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,520
actually

30
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,720
colluded against me.

31
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,280
Angwei,

32
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,360
Ou Shaowen.

33
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,000
Don't think that

34
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,000
by taking over Sihai Group,

35
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,720
you've won.

36
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,680
My guards

37
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,160
only take orders from me.

38
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,280
Do you dare to shoot?

39
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,160
I dare.

40
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,760
Danpa.

41
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,760
You killed my parents

42
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,360
and Aunt Chen Qian.

43
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,240
For these lives,

44
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:45,130
I want you to pay for them yourself.

45
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:58,120
They say you raise children to care for you in old age.

46
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,120
I raised you

47
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,080
and Aung Wei.

48
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,980
But you're all ungrateful wretches.

49
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,840
I was careless.

50
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,720
Sister Hua.

51
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,180
Sister Hua.

52
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:20,800
Stay still. Don't move.

53
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,480
Sister Hua.

54
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,440
Sister Hua.

55
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,240
Lingling.

56
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,640
Don't cry.

57
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,920
You won't look pretty if you cry.

58
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,760
Do you still remember

59
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,640
rule number 25 of the training camp?

60
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,440
Never

61
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,760
show mercy to the enemy.

62
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,120
But when I went back,

63
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,020
I thought about it for a long time.

64
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,600
You were never my enemy.

65
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,200
Lingling.

66
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,360
I want to

67
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,080
let go of the hatred.

68
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,570
You should let it go too.

69
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,120
Can you?

70
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,920
Promise me.

71
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,080
I'm sorry.

72
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,320
Sister Hua.

73
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,200
Sister Hua.

74
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,520
Sister Hua.

75
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,320
This worthless guy

76
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:18,640
is probably going to propose to you.

77
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,560
Don't say yes too easily.

78
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:33,720
There's one more thing I need to explain to you.

79
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,200
We didn't tell you our plan

80
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:39,490
because it only looks real if you didn't know.

81
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,060
That way, Danpa would believe it.

82
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,520
Locking you up

83
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,080
was also because

84
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,800
keeping you by my side at that time

85
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,260
was the safest thing to do.

86
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,159
Only by gaining real power in Sihai Group

87
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:54,290
can we have a chance to turn the tables.

88
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,820
I actually figured it out.

89
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,640
That day when you said 'we'.

90
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,170
Before Sister Hua died,

91
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,920
she gave me all this evidence against Danpa.

92
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,650
I will hand it over to the police

93
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,860
and let the law punish him.

94
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,240
Thank you.

95
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,620
If only I could have really kept you here,

96
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,370
that would have been great.

97
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,320
Ou Shaowen!

98
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,000
Ou Shaowen!

99
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,360
Just wait.

100
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,770
He can't even wait a single minute.

101
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,320
So petty.

102
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,940
He really can't wait a single minute.

103
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,480
Go on.

104
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,080
He's waiting for you.

105
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,490
I'll get going then.

106
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,560
Wait a minute.

107
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,280
Ou Shaowen,

108
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,280
