109
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,520
Maybe

110
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,000
this is the best ending.

111
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,720
I got the Leo route

112
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,240
back from Ou Shaowen.

113
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,440
It belongs to the Dai family.

114
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,200
Thank you.

115
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,360
Dailing.

116
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,240
That night,

117
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,800
when I found out

118
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,240
that your parents

119
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,240
were killed by Danpa,

120
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,340
