121
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,640
I hate myself

122
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:47,300
for not being by your side these past five years.

123
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,480
I'm sorry.

124
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:03,560
Well,

125
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,400
I said

126
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:09,000
once I laid the truth in front of you,

127
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,880
you could then decide

128
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:12,740
where our relationship would go.

129
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,200
Marry me.

130
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,300
Young Master Angwei is proposing

131
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,040
with only two roses?

132
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,140
I'll go pick some more.

133
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:40,680
I do.

134
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:06,520
What are you doing?
